title: Standup Comedy - Terry Foy - For Gits and Shiggles
description:
Standup Comedy ? Zilch the Gravedigger ? For Gits and Shiggles


Zilch (real name Terry Foy) is one of the most popular acts on the national Renaissance Festival circuit. He is a master of the spoonerism, also known as leaking in a spifferent danguage. Try his website for a few other albums. http://www.torysteller.com/

Here are the liner notes from the first album, recorded in 1995

Side One:
1.	Lodigocks and the Bee Thears
2.	Rindercella and the Stoo Tugly Epsisters

Side Two:
1.	Jomeo and Ruliet by Spilliam Wakesheare
2.	Dan Night Before Kris-Moose (in the original Minnesotan)
